06-06T14:06:45.000Z","msg":"其實都多野揀嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果條命生得好<br />\n<br />\n讀完出路:<br />\n1) Assistant consultant &mdash;&gt; consultant <br />\n2) ES&mdash;&gt; AEO&mdash;&gt; EO&mdash;&gt; senior EO&mdash;&gt; enviro manger (通常要連埋safety嗰邊 可以行埋iso做internal audit)<br />\n3) enviro engineer <br />\n4) BIM/ autoCAD draftsman 多個技能多個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5) green building/sustain <br />\n6) 做researcher<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7) Environ policy 嗰啲<br />\n8) 對環保好有熱誠唔介意份糧嘅話就NGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n....仲有冇其他？<br />\n<br />\n有得揀就一定係1,2,3,5 初初人工少 但至少做落去都還好 最緊要係要揾到間有行schemeA嘅公司<br />\n<br />\nGrad之後仲要join做唔同institutions 嘅member讀好多cert (beam pro, iso, EO cert, safety, blah blah..........)先有機會多啲人工"},{"pid":"b00e1346511c6cc54e9fef6e2ce8c1a9daa8ef73","tid":2046680,"uid":206359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79724ac8cd647fe65be310be94b77f82c9c8c7a","tid":2046680,"uid":340004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b566208bbf82f5b06513af07b92d224548ce8aec","tid":2046680,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22228f760a2fad76e9e5477b9509ae232995fe98","tid":2046680,"uid":206359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:30:57.000Z","msg":"入enviro 悔終生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"入science 悔終生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇得揀焗住入sci仲慘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:07:28.000Z","msg":"讀邊間？"},{"pid":"9ae792989bf3ed44057793b36d724d08ef4aabf8","tid":2046680,"uid":340004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b00e1346511c6cc54e9fef6e2ce8c1a9daa8ef73","tid":2046680,"uid":206359,"like":0,"dislik